These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, fanta, almond-milk, iced-tea
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, fishing, collecting, baking
1. the person drinking fanta is between the person drinking soy-milk and the person who's hobby is fishing##2
2. the person drinking fanta is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is card-games##3
3. the person drinking fanta is somewhere between the person drinking iced-tea and the person drinking soy-milk##7
4. the person who's hobby is fishing is in an even position##4
5. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
6. the person who's hobby is fishing is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2     |       3       |      4      |
| Beverage   | almond-milk | iced-tea       | fanta | soy-milk        |
| Hobby      | collecting  | fishing | baking        | card-games |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-2::.
4 different pets are kept: lizard, ferret, rabbit, chinchilla
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: sailing, biathlon, skiing, parkour
1. the person who's sport is parkour is somewhere between the person who's sport is skiing and the owner of the rabbit##7
2. the owner of the chinchilla is somewhere to the left of the owner of the lizard##5
3. the owner of the chinchilla is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is parkour##5
4. the owner of the ferret is on the left of the owner of the chinchilla##1
5. the person who's sport is parkour is between the person who's sport is skiing and the person who's sport is biathlon##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |       3       |    4    |
| Pet     | rabbit | ferret       | chinchilla         | lizard     |
| Sport   | biathlon   | parkour | skiing | sailing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-3::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: superhero, animation, zombie, action
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: hip-hop, r&b, electronic, rock
1. the person watching superhero movies is on the right of the fan of rock##1
2. the fan of rock is somewhere between the fan of r&b and the fan of hip-hop##7
3. the fan of electronic is on the left of the person watching action movies##1
4. the fan of hip-hop is somewhere between the fan of rock and the person watching animation movies##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2      |    3    |    4    |
| Movie-Genre   | animation | action | zombie | superhero  |
| Music-Genre   | electronic | hip-hop  | rock   | r&b |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-4::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: reading, baking, singing, gardening
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: rowing, biathlon, sailing, lacrosse
1. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who's hobby is reading is somewhere between the person who's sport is biathlon and the person who's hobby is gardening##7
3. the person who's hobby is singing is the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
4. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
5. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left of the person who's sport is rowing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |     2      |       3       |      4      |
| Hobby   | baking | reading | gardening       | singing |
| Sport   | biathlon      | rowing   | sailing | lacrosse  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-5::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: woodworking, filmmaking, fishing, collecting
There are 4 different nationalities: colombian, argentine, malaysian, french
1. the french is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##3
2. the colombian is somewhere to the left of the argentine##5
3. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the right of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
4. the french is somewhere between the person who's hobby is filmmaking and the person who's hobby is woodworking##7
5. the french is on the left of the malaysian##1
6. the argentine is somewhere to the left of the french##5
7. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is fishing##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Hobby         | fishing | woodworking   | collecting | filmmaking |
| Nationality   | colombian      | argentine | french      | malaysian |

