.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-6::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, cola, tea, hot-chocolate
There are 4 different nationalities: turkish, thai, egyptian, australian
1. the person drinking tea is on the left of the egyptian##1
2. the egyptian is the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
3. the thai is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
4. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
5. the person drinking cola is on the left or right of the australian##3
6. the australian is somewhere between the turkish and the thai##7
7. the egyptian is somewhere to the right of the person drinking tea##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Beverage      | cola | iced-tea      | tea | hot-chocolate     |
| Nationality   | turkish    | australian | thai   | egyptian |

