.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-7::.
There 4 different types of food: cauliflower, kale, carrot, corn
There are 4 different nationalities: french, japanese, british, russian
1. the french is on the far left##1
2. the person eating kale is on the left of the japanese##1
3. the person eating corn is on the far left or far right##3
4. the russian is somewhere between the person eating cauliflower and the person eating carrot##7
5. the british is somewhere to the left of the person eating carrot##5
6. the russian is on the left or right of the british##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| Food          | corn    | cauliflower   | kale | carrot  |
| Nationality   | french | british | russian    | japanese |

