.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-8::.
There are 4 different nationalities: japanese, thai, russian, indonesian
4 different pets are kept: frog, hedgehog, mouse, lizard
1. the thai is not the owner of the lizard##6
2. the owner of the mouse is on the left or right of the owner of the lizard##3
3. the indonesian is the owner of the mouse##1
4. the russian is somewhere between the indonesian and the japanese##7
5. the thai is on the left of the japanese##1
6. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the owner of the mouse##1
7. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the owner of the frog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |    4     |
| Nationality   | indonesian | russian | thai | japanese |
| Pet           | mouse   | lizard    | frog       | hedgehog  |

