.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-9::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  teacher, software-developer, pilot, dancer
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: salsa, ambient, gospel, metal
1. the teacher is not the fan of salsa##6
2. the pilot is on the right of the teacher##1
3. the fan of salsa is on the left or right of the teacher##3
4. the teacher is on the right of the fan of metal##1
5. the pilot is somewhere between the fan of metal and the software-developer##7
6. the fan of ambient is somewhere to the right of the fan of gospel##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |     3     |       4        |
| Job           | dancer | teacher | pilot | software-developer |
| Music-Genre   | metal         | gospel      | salsa | ambient            |

