.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-10::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, epic, drama, fantasy
4 different pets are kept: turtle, goat, hedgehog, rabbit
1. the person watching fantasy movies is somewhere between the person watching adventure movies and the owner of the rabbit##7
2. the person watching epic movies is not the owner of the hedgehog##6
3. the owner of the goat is not the person watching drama movies##6
4. the person watching drama movies is somewhere to the right of the owner of the rabbit##5
5. the person watching adventure movies is the owner of the turtle##1
6. the person watching fantasy movies is somewhere to the right of the owner of the turtle##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |   3    |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure | fantasy | epic | drama |
| Pet           | turtle    | goat   | rabbit  | hedgehog      |

