.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-11::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: satire, romance, comedy, drama
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: metal, classical, techno, disco
1. the fan of disco is somewhere to the right of the fan of metal##5
2. the fan of techno is on the left of the fan of metal##1
3. the fan of classical is somewhere to the left of the person watching comedy movies##5
4. the person watching drama movies is on the left of the person watching satire movies##1
5. the person watching satire movies is between the person watching romance movies and the fan of classical##2
6. the fan of techno is somewhere between the fan of classical and the person watching romance movies##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |      3      |   4    |
| Movie-Genre   | drama | satire | romance | comedy   |
| Music-Genre   | classical    | techno      | metal      | disco |

