1. the person who's sport is surfing is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is badminton##5
2. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
3. the person who's sport is badminton is not the person who's hobby is filmmaking##6
4. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left of the person who's sport is cricket##1
5. the person who's sport is water-polo is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is surfing##5
6. the person who's hobby is video-games is somewhere between the person who's hobby is filmmaking and the person who's hobby is singing##7

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2      |      3      |    4    |
| Hobby   | singing | video-games | fishing | filmmaking |
| Sport   | badminton  | cricket    | surfing    | water-polo  |

