.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-13::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: baking, reading, puzzles, video-games
The people use 4 different means of transport: jet-ski, quad-bike, van, airplane
1. the person driving the quad-bike is on the right of the person who's hobby is baking##1
2. the person who's hobby is video-games is the person driving the jet-ski##1
3. the person driving the van is the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
4. the person who's hobby is puzzles is not the person driving the quad-bike##6
5. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the right of the person driving the quad-bike##1
6. the person driving the quad-bike is somewhere between the person driving the jet-ski and the person who's hobby is puzzles##7
7. the person who's hobby is reading is somewhere to the left of the person driving the van##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| Hobby       | video-games | baking | reading | puzzles |
| Transport   | jet-ski   | airplane      | quad-bike        | van  |

