.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-14::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, almond-milk, soy-milk, iced-tea
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: disco, classical, folk, country
1. the fan of classical is in an even position##4
2. the fan of country is somewhere between the person drinking iced-tea and the fan of folk##7
3. the fan of country is on the left or right of the person drinking iced-tea##3
4. the fan of folk is in an even position##4
5. the person drinking lemonade is somewhere to the left of the fan of classical##5
6. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the fan of folk##1
7. the person drinking almond-milk is the fan of country##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |   3   |    4    |
| Beverage      | lemonade   | soy-milk | almond-milk | iced-tea   |
| Music-Genre   | disco | folk   | country | classical |

