3. the dressmaker is on the far left##1
4. the person who's hobby is writing is not the dressmaker##6
5. the person who's hobby is fishing is somewhere between the entrepreneur and the doctor##7

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |     2      |      3      |       4       |
