.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-20::.
4 different pets are kept: mouse, pony, chinchilla, goat
The people use 4 different means of transport: ship, car, train, helicopter
1. the owner of the chinchilla is somewhere between the person driving the ship and the owner of the pony##7
2. the person driving the ship is on the right of the person driving the car##1
3. the owner of the goat is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1
4. the person driving the car is somewhere to the right of the owner of the chinchilla##5
5. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left or right of the person driving the train##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2     |     3     |  4  |
| Pet         | pony    | chinchilla | goat     | mouse |
| Transport   | train | helicopter  | car | ship |

 